<p>A speedboat carrying migrants collided with a Hellenic Coast Guard patrol vessel off the Greek island of Chios in the eastern Aegean Sea, killing at least 15 people, Greek authorities said. Rescuers recovered bodies from the water and brought survivors to safety, while search-and-rescue teams kept looking for anyone still missing. Greek authorities said investigators are still working to determine exactly how the two vessels collided.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/saUbymtKhHQV576SkXp6_qvXnlwSUrhfk19t_iFi_ZJ4hzn8BSSrZug_iiQrcro-j-xXPXYjxbEQ-56pqzkugsMKB6dg0v-cZy140ne3cDZ5Ts3e0kpTncrnnRhF4LWhr-LkbI0eW0CsZkhk0wZ8_XgaBg2k1g6Pg30vE_8YzId-Q1a-31e4wBzi2mR1UJlo' alt='Emergency workers on the eastern Aegean island of Chios, Greece, on Wednesday. The exact circumstances of the collision were not immediately clear.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Rescues reported: The coast guard said it pulled 25 migrants from the water, including about 11 children, after the collision.</li><li>Victim details: The coastguard said it recovered 14 bodies (SCMP reported 11 men and three women), while some outlets cited a higher overall death toll.</li><li>Search assets: Greek officials and media reports said the search involved multiple coast guard patrol vessels, an air force helicopter, and a private boat carrying divers.</li><li>Capsize reported: Reuters said the migrant boat capsized after colliding with the coast guard vessel.</li><li>Injuries reported: ABC News said more than two dozen people were injured in the incident.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Hellenic Coast Guard: Greek authorities said search-and-rescue crews were still working the area after the crash, as they looked for any passengers who might be missing. (<a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/greek-rescuers-search-potential-missing-people-after-deadly-129840123'>ABC News</a>)</li><li>BBC report: The BBC said the coastguard reported a pursuit was under way at the time of the collision near Chios. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cdre825p110o'>BBC</a>)</li><li>Deutsche Welle report: DW said that after the patrol boat sent a warning signal, the migrant boat tried to get away, and the collision followed for reasons that are still unclear. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/migrant-boat-collides-with-greek-coast-guard-vessel-15-dead/a-75791389'>Deutsche Welle</a>)</li><li>New York Times framing: The New York Times described the crash as unusual in the Aegean, where deaths more often come from storm-related sinkings than from vessel-to-vessel collisions. (<a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/04/world/europe/15-dead-migrant-clash-collision-greece.html'>The New York Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2026/02/04/greek-coast-guard-vessel-and-speedboat-carrying-migrants-collide-killing-15-people'>Greek coast guard vessel and speedboat carrying migrants collide, killing 15 people</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/greek-rescuers-search-potential-missing-people-after-deadly-129840123'>Greek rescuers search for potential missing people after deadly migrant boat collision</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/europe/article/3342296/least-15-killed-collision-between-migrant-speedboat-and-greek-coastguard-vessel'>At least 15 dead after migrant speedboat and Greek coastguard vessel collide</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/feb/03/collision-between-greek-coastguard-patrol-and-boat-carrying-migrants'>Collision between Greek coastguard patrol and migrant boat kills 14</a> - theguardian.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/migrant-boat-collides-with-greek-coast-guard-vessel-15-dead/a-75791389'>Migrant boat collides with Greek coast guard vessel, 15 dead</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.cbsnews.com/news/greece-coast-guard-ship-migrant-boat-collide-death-toll/'>Greek coast guard ship